### UniFi Network Controller API Explorer
### Use the REST Client extension to test API endpoints directly in VS Code
### Variables are defined in .vscode/settings.json

@baseUrl = https://localhost:8443
@site = default

### 1. Login (Get Cookie)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "your-username",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### 2. Get Self Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/self
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 3. List Sites
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/self/sites
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 4. Get Site Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/stat/sites
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 5. List Devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/stat/device
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 6. List Active Clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/stat/sta
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 7. List All Users (Including Inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/rest/user
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 8. Get Alarms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/list/alarm
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 9. Get Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/stat/event
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 10. Get Network Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/rest/networkconf
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 11. Get WLAN Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/s/{{site}}/rest/wlanconf
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

### 12. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/logout
Cookie: {{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}
